{"tid":734630,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Mesh Wifi同Repeater有咩分別","createTime":"2018-07-08T20:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T14:06:31.000Z","uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ded5f64ad3436ffc502fb75504bb0de4f9f8d8e4","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T20:10:22.000Z","msg":"屋企3房<br />\n<br />\n廳｜房1 |||| 房2 | 房3|<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁 房1同2中間係主力牆<br />\n而加係Router係房1<br />\n平時係房2都收得好差 所以想加多個Router係2到<br />\n但係我想問下Mesh Wi-Fi<br />\n同我拉線加多個Router做Repeater有無分別<br />\n如果我用MeshWi-Fi 係咪可以加強到我係房2收信號嘅效果？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d091983517768de2162ef69e1ddf8351d4b08855","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T20:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086fb2fb4f820a7d2c8b1b237299184a805085ae","tid":734630,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T20:26:54.000Z","msg":"用homeplug啦"},{"pid":"a6d4424cf37d7f0599babe334f23f6b3f2871518","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"086fb2fb4f820a7d2c8b1b237299184a805085ae","tid":734630,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T20:26:54.000Z","msg":"用homeplug啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T20:44:10.000Z","msg":"homeplug插拖把會唔會有干擾"},{"pid":"138bc2bdcf1511f02c20d9c77ef2c21b0418002d","tid":734630,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6d4424cf37d7f0599babe334f23f6b3f2871518","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"086fb2fb4f820a7d2c8b1b237299184a805085ae","tid":734630,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T20:26:54.000Z","msg":"用homeplug啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T20:44:10.000Z","msg":"homeplug插拖把會唔會有干擾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T20:48:36.000Z","msg":"防雷拖把就會"},{"pid":"1aabbe1e0cc3775e6c55ac18e1043fe818522251","tid":734630,"uid":19208,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T23:45:29.000Z","msg":"簡單講repeater 速度會減半<br />\nMesh 會保持高速"},{"pid":"2b87caf45548db3fbc23e59bb3988035af8d2019","tid":734630,"uid":35092,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:08:14.000Z","msg":"Mesh 需要拉線入房，Repeater 唔需要。"},{"pid":"698c096eb3955dfbc6ec4e7060630cc34814513a","tid":734630,"uid":193950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:55:13.000Z","msg":"最大分別係Mesh識跳完一隻再一隻"},{"pid":"1cb71d968dbbfab0e79c392c481fdd444365a89e","tid":734630,"uid":193950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b87caf45548db3fbc23e59bb3988035af8d2019","tid":734630,"uid":35092,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:08:14.000Z","msg":"Mesh 需要拉線入房，Repeater 唔需要。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:58:14.000Z","msg":"Mesh嘅運作原理就係可以用無線做主幹, 跳完一隻再跳一隻，有啲Mesh根本唔support拉線做trunk"},{"pid":"0f4335f3189980397129f62365cb41d2690e327b","tid":734630,"uid":109690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:05:42.000Z","msg":"用緊orbi 都係set 係房2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你當打個六折啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都好夠用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲下加多個satellite 係房1睇下效果如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原本想係廁所都加個satellite<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家主人房都係用返之前剩落嚟個套netgear powerline <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67dd3c28c77a1b789aa26e8878da572e54ce52f","tid":734630,"uid":14623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"mesh wifi 係一間屋裏面有e.g 3個router，大家都溝通到，確保你屋既一角到另一角都有好既signal<br />\n<br />\nrepeater 係一間屋裡有1個router作為main hub，然後repeater只係張main hub發出及signal 加強再rebroadcast<br />\n<br />\n佢地最主要分別係前者冇main hub，有redundancy所以可以成間屋都有好既signal，而後者只係rebroadcast，屋角signal會有機會弱"},{"pid":"1296d6428ea89bec5f66ac51ed2b69bfe4bbb31e","tid":734630,"uid":35092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cb71d968dbbfab0e79c392c481fdd444365a89e","tid":734630,"uid":193950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b87caf45548db3fbc23e59bb3988035af8d2019","tid":734630,"uid":35092,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:08:14.000Z","msg":"Mesh 需要拉線入房，Repeater 唔需要。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:58:14.000Z","msg":"Mesh嘅運作原理就係可以用無線做主幹, 跳完一隻再跳一隻，有啲Mesh根本唔support拉線做trunk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:24:06.000Z","msg":"Mesh 本身個 design 用意唔係咁 ...<br />\n<br />\nMesh 一開頭個 design 就係 extend 個 cover，從而令到 device 由一隻跳去另外一隻可以保持連線，而唔斷 ..."},{"pid":"c46309d30c66ac7732fc16688131860f0ae3e4cb","tid":734630,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a67dd3c28c77a1b789aa26e8878da572e54ce52f","tid":734630,"uid":14623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"mesh wifi 係一間屋裏面有e.g 3個router，大家都溝通到，確保你屋既一角到另一角都有好既signal<br />\n<br />\nrepeater 係一間屋裡有1個router作為main hub，然後repeater只係張main hub發出及signal 加強再rebroadcast<br />\n<br />\n佢地最主要分別係前者冇main hub，有redundancy所以可以成間屋都有好既signal，而後者只係rebroadcast，屋角signal會有機會弱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/092514_7c20664bc1291588776a9ea622268980.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F092514_7c20664bc1291588776a9ea622268980.png&h=1e930c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nrepeater收到既signal已經弱左，rebroadcast既會更加弱<br />\n<br />\n伸：9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d13781f9e297e4b9955d6d75af5a4d60a876eb4","tid":734630,"uid":130595,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:28:55.000Z","msg":"mesh 同 repeater 咪一鳩樣, 純粹改個名賣貴d<br />\n<br />\n話mesh 無main... 插broadband線果隻咪係main, 你3隻mesh 唔撚駛插broadband 線就上到網 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外兩隻咪就係repeater, 有撚分別"},{"pid":"eb3a8cc79f5cb48f533b540e1cfb681c8db677e3","tid":734630,"uid":130595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c46309d30c66ac7732fc16688131860f0ae3e4cb","tid":734630,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a67dd3c28c77a1b789aa26e8878da572e54ce52f","tid":734630,"uid":14623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"mesh wifi 係一間屋裏面有e.g 3個router，大家都溝通到，確保你屋既一角到另一角都有好既signal<br />\n<br />\nrepeater 係一間屋裡有1個router作為main hub，然後repeater只係張main hub發出及signal 加強再rebroadcast<br />\n<br />\n佢地最主要分別係前者冇main hub，有redundancy所以可以成間屋都有好既signal，而後者只係rebroadcast，屋角signal會有機會弱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/092514_7c20664bc1291588776a9ea622268980.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F092514_7c20664bc1291588776a9ea622268980.png&h=1e930c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nrepeater收到既signal已經弱左，rebroadcast既會更加弱<br />\n<br />\n伸：9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"mesh 同 repeater 咪一樣用緊wifi 去連<br />\n點解mesh 會強, repeater 會弱"},{"pid":"18c995a33cf003d1909c9434479d79a302a2b177","tid":734630,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:36:29.000Z","msg":"其實我都覺得無咩分別<br />\n本身訊號弱有牆阻隔既地方一樣係慢<br />\n我諗用repeater 同mesh wifi 速度上唔會差得遠<br />\n最唔同既地方係應該mesh 識自動幫你轉用邊個router 既訊號<br />\nrepeater 就算你SET 同一個SSID, 都要去到無晒訊號先識同你轉第2個ROUTER<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"60fd8cbf45de531e6258fc7d8ab9f0bef02eb106","tid":734630,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:40:20.000Z","msg":"硬件上無分別<br />\n<br />\nmesh 叫做d 廠整好for dummy, 輕鬆 setup<br />\n<br />\n唔識既話, 呢d 錢無得慳<br />\n<br />\n識既自己買幾隻tri-band routers 駁埋效果更好"},{"pid":"7744187ed87a05686b42800574103785f7afe288","tid":734630,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aabbe1e0cc3775e6c55ac18e1043fe818522251","tid":734630,"uid":19208,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T23:45:29.000Z","msg":"簡單講repeater 速度會減半<br />\nMesh 會保持高速"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"隔咗個主力牆都係會收得差，低速<br />\n由其5g基本上穿唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4058ae6b717f75d36a02d93dea40b691d0bb17","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n我本身D信號穿完主力牆之後都含曬撚（訓係到比我個身擋住直頭收唔到）<br />\n係咪一定要拉線先解決到？"},{"pid":"2aa7937594d864d83cb4f0f705f0f855e8514633","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4058ae6b717f75d36a02d93dea40b691d0bb17","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n我本身D信號穿完主力牆之後都含曬撚（訓係到比我個身擋住直頭收唔到）<br />\n係咪一定要拉線先解決到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"如果個信號穿完主力牆之後已經弱左<br />\n係主力牆後面就算用Repeater定Mesh係咪都救唔番"},{"pid":"977d8c9536cfce9b0981107d3a7c68aba78155da","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5fb189ddf62528fa4428a0dcc4d6ba6eccdd72","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f028692b4fe2f696b126a1d765141fb8a41746","tid":734630,"uid":23063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa7937594d864d83cb4f0f705f0f855e8514633","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4058ae6b717f75d36a02d93dea40b691d0bb17","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n我本身D信號穿完主力牆之後都含曬撚（訓係到比我個身擋住直頭收唔到）<br />\n係咪一定要拉線先解決到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"如果個信號穿完主力牆之後已經弱左<br />\n係主力牆後面就算用Repeater定Mesh係咪都救唔番"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"係, 其實repeater 用同一個channel 去同主router 同client 一齊用, 所以會慢左. 而mesh 會有獨立channel 去同主router 溝通, 而你上網就用另一條chaanel, 所以mesh 會快左少少<br />\n利申鳩吹"},{"pid":"ff68f00e88ba7cd652704e8fe67f845ae0b88ee9","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39f028692b4fe2f696b126a1d765141fb8a41746","tid":734630,"uid":23063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa7937594d864d83cb4f0f705f0f855e8514633","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4058ae6b717f75d36a02d93dea40b691d0bb17","tid":734630,"uid":15613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n我本身D信號穿完主力牆之後都含曬撚（訓係到比我個身擋住直頭收唔到）<br />\n係咪一定要拉線先解決到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"如果個信號穿完主力牆之後已經弱左<br />\n係主力牆後面就算用Repeater定Mesh係咪都救唔番"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"係, 其實repeater 用同一個channel 去同主router 同client 一齊用, 所以會慢左. 而mesh 會有獨立channel 去同主router 溝通, 而你上網就用另一條chaanel, 所以mesh 會快左少少<br />\n利申鳩吹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:17:59.000Z","msg":"所以我都係拉線拉多個repeater去主力牆另一邊<br />\nright？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f82686d94246d9dfbca10b6ff3fbb9668d7951","tid":734630,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"早排家用wifi 轉左 mesh<br />\n<br />\nbridge mode<br />\n本身隻router 繼續用<br />\nwifi就交比另一套mesh<br />\n<br />\nset 好一隻bridge<br />\n三隻兩隻有插lan<br />\n<br />\n插lan嗰兩隻去到100M出街<br />\n<br />\n唔插嗰隻就6-70M<br />\n<br />\nps,隻mesh係最cheap 嘅tenda mw3<br />\ncable 係行得10/100<br />\n<br />\n主要咁換係<br />\n<br />\nwifi屋企本身收唔晒<br />\n要兩隻wifi router<br />\n但房入廳咁唔識自己switch 就好煩<br />\n<br />\n但我對wifi speed 要求唔高<br />\n行到100M其實覩夠晒<br />\n呢隻tenda真係平<br />\n<br />\n五舊唔洗攪掂<br />\n<br />\n抵用<br />\n<br />\n另外佢真银好易set<br />\n<br />\n前後五分鐘乜都攪掂"}]}